picker-up
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a member of a shearing team who picks up fleeces from shearing board.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
